            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>with some of the <strong>chopped coriander </strong>and season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>coriander yoghurt</strong></p><p>Combine the<strong> grated carrot</strong>,<strong> tomato wedges</strong> and<strong> remaining chopped coriander</strong> with your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> in a bowl – this is your<strong> carrot & tomato salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
