    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> Turkish-style spiced lean beef borek</strong> with the <strong>bulgur</strong>,<strong> carrot & tomato salad</strong> and <strong>coriander yoghurt</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
